---
import Layout from '../../templates/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Plan Your Trip" description="Visas, borders, seasons, packing list and travel tips.">
  <main class="container section">
    <h1 class="h1">Plan Your Trip</h1>
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 mt-6">
      <section>
        <h2 class="h3">Best seasons</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Dolphins year‑round; whales July–November; turtles Nov–Feb.</p>
        <h2 class="h3 mt-8">Documents & border</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Have all passports ready for both sides of the Kosi Bay border; Mozambique side requires vehicle papers if self‑driving.</p>
        <h2 class="h3 mt-8">Health</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Southern Mozambique is a low‑risk malaria area—consult your health professional.</p>
      </section>
      <aside class="card p-6">
        <h3 class="h3">Packing list</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Reef‑safe sunscreen, hat, long‑sleeve rash vest</li>
          <li>Snorkel gear (optional—rentals available)</li>
          <li>Cash for markets & tips (ZAR/MZN)</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
